		description : "This book is covered in fine leather, with a symbol of a harp stamped onto the spine. On the inside cover is the inscription: \"Thanks for getting the books for me. Hopefully we meet again. — O. E.\" The spellbook & anything written on its pages can't be damaged by fire or water & doesn't deteriorate with age.",
