		description: "This silky black cloak is clearly of drow manufacture & loses its magic if exposed to sunlight for 1 hr uninterrupted. While worn, Wis (Perception) checks made to notice me have disadv. & I have adv. on Dex (Stealth) checks.",
		descriptionFull: "This silky black cloak is clearly of drow manufacture & loses its magic if exposed to sunlight for 1 hr uninterrupted.\n   While you wear this cloak, Wisdom (Perception) checks made to perceive you have Disadvantage, and you have Advantage on Dexterity (Stealth) checks.",
