		descriptionFull : "This cloak defaults to jet black leather with a stylized yellow hawk near the neck clasp. While wearing the cloak, the bearer can speak and understand Deep Speech.\n   While wearing this cloak, you can take a Bonus Action to change the style, color, and apparent quality of the garment. The cloak's weight doesn't change. Regardless of its appearance, the cloak can't be anything but a cloak. Although it can duplicate the appearance of other magic cloaks, it doesn't gain their magical properties.",
