		rarity : "common",
		description : "This cloak is fine black silk with a stylized rainbow dragon face. As a bonus action, it sheds 10-ft bright light & 10-ft more dim, or stops. Another bonus action changes the cloak's style, color & apparent quality. Its weight doesn't change and can look like other magic cloaks, but doesn't gain their properties.",
		descriptionFull : "This cloak defaults to a stylized rainbow dragon face on a background of fine black silk.\n   " + toUni("Beacon") + ". You can take a Bonus Action to cause the item to shed Bright Light in a 10-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 10 feet, or to extinguish the light.\n   While wearing this cloak, you can take a Bonus Action to change the style, color, and apparent quality of the garment. The cloak's weight doesn't change. Regardless of its appearance, the cloak can't be anything but a cloak. Although it can duplicate the appearance of other magic cloaks, it doesn't gain their magical properties.",
