		rarity : "common",
		description : "This olive green poncho is styled in the fashion favored by gunslingers. Geometric patterns are embroidered into the cloth with white thread. As a bonus action while wearing this cloak, I can change its style, color, and apparent quality but not its weight. It can look like other magic cloaks, but doesn't gain their properties. I also suffer no harm in extreme temps past 0\u00B0F & 100\u00B0F",
