		description : "This flask is shaped like a potion vial, with a large nozzle affixed to the stopper. The crossed axes & elk emblem of the Fireseeker Task Force is stamped on the side. As a Magic action, open it \u0026 speak a command word, pouring out fresh/salt water until my next turn. \"Stream\" for 1 gal. \"Fountain\" for 5 gal. \"Geyser\" for 30 gal in 30 ft \xD7 1 ft line. While held, aim line at 1 target. Creature makes DC 13 Str save or 1d4 Bludgeoning & Prone. If unattended object up to 200 lbs, knocked over.",
		descriptionLong : "This flask is shaped like a potion vial, with a large nozzle affixed to the stopper. The crossed axes and elk emblem of the Fireseeker Task Force is stamped on the vial. As a Magic action, I can remove the stopper & speak a command word, pouring out fresh or salt water (my choice) until my next turn starts. \"Splash\" produces 1 gallon. \"Fountain\" produces 5 gallons. \"Geyser\" produces 30 gallons that gush out in a line 30-ft long by 1-ft wide. While held, I can aim the line in 1 direction to hit target. If creature, makes a DC 13 STR save or takes 1d4 Bludgeoning & falls Prone. If unattended object up to 200 lbs, I knock it over.",
