		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "This 6-ft diameter piece of fine red silk can be folded into a handkerchief, scarf, or cloak. When studied, the folds seem to dance & flicker like fire. It lets me speak Ignan. Magic action to unfold cloth & put on solid surface, where it becomes a 10-ft deep extradimensional hole. Repeat action to remove & refold. The space is always the same, so I can store items & creatures (1 hr air). DC 10 Str (Athletics) to escape. It can't be used to create passages.",
		descriptionLong : "This 6-ft diameter piece of fine red silk can be folded into a handkerchief, scarf, or cloak. When studied closely, the folds of silk seem to dance & flicker like fire. While on my person, I can speak Ignan. As a Magic action, I can unfold the cloth and place it on a solid surface, whereupon it creates a 10-ft deep extradimensional hole. It can't be used to create passages. Repeat action to remove and refold. The space is always the same, so I can store objects and creatures there. The hole weighs next to nothing & holds 1 hr of air (divided by #). Creatures inside the folded hole can escape as an action with a DC 10 Str (Athletics) check, appearing next to me if they do. Placing the hole in a similar extradimensional item space instantly destroys both and opens a one-way gate to the Astral Plane.",
