		source : [["AL","SJ-DC"]],
		rarity : "common",
		description : "This shimmering silver metal tankard has intricate carvings of waves and sea creatures that seem to move slightly from the corner of my eye. The handle is shaped like twisting seaweed and embedded with tiny pearls. A faint glow emanates from inside the tankard, like the bioluminescence of deep sea creatures. As a bonus action, it sheds 10-ft bright light & 10-ft more dim, or stops. I can drink ale, wine, or other alcoholic beverages from the tankard without getting drunk. It has no effect on magical liquids or harmful substances such as poison.",
		descriptionFull : "This ornate tankard is crafted from a shimmering, silvery metal, adorned with intricate carvings of waves and sea creatures that seem to move ever so slightly when observed from the corner of one's eye. The handle is shaped like a twisting seaweed strand, with tiny pearls embedded along its length. A faint, luminescent glow emanates from within the tankard, reminiscent of the bioluminescent glow of deep-sea creatures.\n   " + toUni("Beacon") + ". You can take a Bonus Action to cause the item to shed Bright Light in a 10-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 10 feet, or to extinguish the light.\n   This tankard has a stern face sculpted into one side. You can drink ale, wine, or any other nonmagical alcoholic beverage poured into it without becoming inebriated. The tankard has no effect on magical liquids or harmful substances such as poison.",
