		recovery : "dawn",
		action : ["action", "Choose Unknown Cantrip (8 hrs)"],
		description : "This strange screwdriver has a button on one end. When it's pressed, the end extends outward, a small light turns on and the tool makes a whirling noise. Exactly what this does is mysterious. While holding the screwdriver, I gain a +1 bonus to spell atk rolls & saving throw DCs of my artificer spells. As an action, I can transform it into any type of artisan's tool. Once per day as an action, I can choose any cantrip I don't know & cast it as an artificer cantrip for 8 hrs.",
