		name : "Bands of the Black Unicorn (Iron Bands of Bilarro)",
		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "Any time I have the opportunity to pursue vengeance against those who've violated my ideals, this iron sphere heightens the urge. As a Magic action once per dawn, make a ranged atk (Dex + Prof). The bands expand & display the image of Bilarro's black unicorn banner. If hit, up to Huge creature is Restrained until I use a bonus action. Once per 24 hrs, an action DC 20 Str (Athletics) chk can destroy the bands to free them.",
		descriptionLong : "Any time the bearer of this iron sphere has the opportunity to pursue vengeance against those who've violated their ideals, it heightens the urge. As a Magic action once per dawn, I can throw the sphere at a Huge or smaller creature. The bands expand & display the image of Bilarro's black unicorn banner. I make a ranged atk roll with an atk bonus equal to my Dex modifier + Proficiency Bonus. On a hit, the target is Restrained until I use a bonus action to release it. Doing so, or missing, makes the bands contract back into a sphere. Once per day, a creature can make a DC 20 Str (Athletics) chk as an action, freeing the target & destroying the bands on a success.",
