		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "With green plumage & a golden quill & shaft, this oversized feather is considered a good luck charm. Thora's grandfather told her it came from a magnificent gentle griffon that roamed the skies around Forheim. As a Magic action while outside, I can touch it to an empty space on the ground. The token disappears & a 60-ft nonmagical oak tree springs into existence. The trunk has a 5-ft diameter & its branches spread out in a 20-ft radius.",
