		description : "This pipe is made of dark wood & inlaid mithral with a stem fashioned from a hollow leg bone once belonging to a bird. When used, it creates a random bird call. While smoking the pipe, Magic action to exhale a puff of smoke that takes the form of a creature, such as a dragon or flumph. The form must fit in a 1-ft cube & loses its shape after a few seconds, becoming an ordinary puff of smoke.",
