		descriptionFull : "This doll, fished from the lagoon near The Couatl's Blessing, has been stained green by exposure to algae for who knows how long, and catoblepas corruption more recently. Its hair has half fallen out, and it carries a permanent septic smell.\n   While this doll is within 5 feet of you, you can spend a Short Rest telling it to say up to six phrases, none of which can be more than six words long, and set a condition under which the doll speaks each phrase. You can also replace old phrases with new ones. Whatever the condition, it must occur within 5 feet of the doll to make it speak. For example, whenever someone picks up the doll, it might say, “I want a piece of candy.” The doll's phrases are lost when your Attunement to the doll ends."
