		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "These spectacles are wrought of thick brass, inset with a row of tiny rubies. A small line of efreeti script inside the band says their place of origin is the City of Brass in the Elemental Plane of Fire. When I focus through the lenses, I see a slight glow from each object I inspect —  the warmer the object, the brighter the glow. I also have Darkvision and advantage on Int (Investigation) chks within 1 ft.",
