		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "These \"Aviator Sunglasses\" are styled after those worn by the Gnomish tinkerers who developed the 1st flying machines. The crystal lenses fit snugly over my eyes & give me a stylish glint & glimmer in a lit area. They're useful as shields from the sun, & help me see clearly in the workshop & at gauges & controls in flight. I have Darkvision and advantage on Int (Investigation) chks within 1 ft.",
		descriptionFull : "These \"Aviator Sunglasses\" are styled after the fashion worn by the Gnomish tinkerers who developed the first flying contraptions. The eyeglasses are useful in everyday wear as shields from direct sunlight, but they can also help you to see clearly in the workshop, and to get a better look at gauges and controls while in flight.\n   These crystal lenses fit snugly over the eyes, and give your countenance a stylish glint and glimmer when you move in a lit area.\n   These crystal lenses fit over the eyes. While wearing them, your vision improves significantly out to a range of 1 foot, granting you Darkvision within that range and Advantage on Intelligence (Investigation) checks made to examine something within that range.",
