			description : "As a Magic action, I can say command & throw one or both of these gold statuettes to an empty space in 60 ft. Each becomes a lion for 1 hr, until I repeat action or it has 0 HP. The lions are twinned pairs of contrast coloration. One white with black stripes, one black with white stripes. They're Friendly, understand my languages, obey my commands, & act directly after me.",
