		description : "These soft-sided boots are made from silk & secured by a hardened-wood buckle near the top. When I take a step, I hear a fragment of an ancient elven song that makes mushrooms in the Velarium glow & webs tense enough for walking without adhesion. As a bonus action, I can click heels to double my walking speed & give Opportunity Atks against me disadv. Another bonus action ends effect. The boots can be used for 10 min, recharging after a long rest.",
