		attunement : true,
		description : "These boots are very soft & have a curled toe in their natural form. The boots are imbued with illusion magic, letting me alter their appearance in minor ways. Such changes don't affect their use or magical properties. As a bonus action, I can click heels to double my walking speed & give Opportunity Atks against me disadv. Another bonus action ends effect. The boots can be used for 10 min, recharging after a long rest.",
