		descriptionFull: "This broad, polished headband is forged of purple stone struck through with veins of mithral. While attuned, the wearer gains the flaw: \"Patience is a virtue; I slowly and ponderously weigh all possible options before acting.\"\n   Your Intelligence is 19 while you wear this headband. It has no effect on you if your Intelligence is 19 or higher without it.",
