		description : "This helm looks like a black-visored barbuta crafted from black iron. It's warm to the touch & sigils of flames cover the surface in shades of red & orange. The helm once belonged to a powerful eldritch knight who was killed in battle with unspeakable evil. It features in a prophecy & whispers to me to become more powerful for the evil might return. While worn, I can cast Comprehend Languages from it. ",
