		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "A hollow silvered tusk carved with bestial images & stained with blood from countless battles, this horn urges me to kill with my bare hands, the taste of congealed blood filling my mouth. As a Magic action once per 7 days, I can blow the horn to summon 2 warrior spirits in 60 ft. These Berserkers are bloodthirsty warriors of Malar immune to Charmed & Frightened, disappear after 1 hr or at 0 HP, are Friendly & follow my commands.",
