		rarity : "legendary",
		description : "This medallion is made of coral and shaped like a crab. It hangs on a kelp necklace. The crab grants adv on saves vs spells and +1 AC. If I fail a save vs a Necromancy spell or harmful Undead effect, I can use 1 charge as a reaction to succeed. The scarab has 12 charges & crumbles into dust once they're gone.",
		descriptionFull : "This particular medallion is made of coral and shaped like a crab. It hangs on a kelp necklace.\n   This beetle-shaped medallion provides three benefits while it is on your person:\n \u2022 " + toUni("Defense") + ". You gain a +1 bonus to Armor Class.\n \u2022 " + toUni("Preservation") + ". The scarab has 12 charges. If you fail a saving throw against a Necromancy spell or a harmful effect originating from an Undead, you can take a Reaction to expend 1 charge and turn the failed save into a successful one. The scarab crumbles into powder and is destroyed when its last charge is expended.\n \u2022 " + toUni("Spell Resistance") + ". You have Advantage on saving throws against spells.",
		attunement: true,
		savetxt: { adv_vs: ["spells"] },
