		descriptionLong : "Glowing with an inner light, this gem flickers in a random pattern that slows as each charge is used. It has 50 charges. As a Magic action while holding it, speak 1 of 3 command words to make it: [1] shed bright light in a 30-ft radius & dim light for 30 ft more until I use another word or end it with a bonus action, [2] fire a 60-ft beam of light at 1 creature (1 charge, DC 15 Con save or Blinded 1 minute), or [3] flare with blinding light in a 30-ft cone (5 charges, DC 15 Con save or Blinded 1 minute). Blinded creatures can repeat the save at the end of each their turns. When all of the gem's charges are used, it becomes a nonmagical jewel worth 50 gp.",
