		source : [["AL","PO"]], // BoMT Chapter 5: Gem
		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "The surface of this gold ring is covered in extremely detailed runework that forms a mazelike pattern. Attempting to follow it never seems to work. The ring bears a fluorite stone and is enchanted to sharpen my mind. It has 3 charges and regains 1d4-1 expended charges daily at dawn. When I make an Intelligence check, I can spend 1 charge to get advantage on the check.",
