		name : "Ring of Spell Storing (DDAL4-8)",
		source : [["AL","S4"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "This plain gold band, tarnished & chipped, can be attuned to in 1 min. Anyone can cast into the ring with a 1st-5th lvl spell slot, which is stored if space. The ring holds 5 lvls of spells. I can cast stored spells from the ring, freeing space, using original caster's atk bonus, save DC, spell modifier, & spell slot lvl. When I cast an arcane spell, I feel cold & faint of breath.",
