		source : [["AL","PS-DC"]],
		rarity : "legendary",
		description : "This ring was made from a rare piece of Tarrasque carapace & wrapped in spell enhanced Mithral by a master craftsman. I can attune to it in 1 min. I have advantage on saves vs spells. Spells up to 7th lvl have no effect if I pass. If that spell targeted only me (no AOEs), reaction to have the spell target the caster instead.",
