		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "This unassuming chunk of bauxite is carved in the shape of a round mother goddess & seems to thrum faintly when held. The thrumming increases to a hypnotic hum when used. Once per dawn when the stone is touching the ground, I can summon an earth elemental as a Magic action. It understands my languages, obeys my commands and acts directly after me. It disappears after 1 hr, at 0 HP or with a bonus action.",
